{
  "stem": "22883.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So he met me and said, why do you don't-- both Liliana and you come with me, and we will sit there.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because the-- the-- the camp was an open field.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So if there would be shooting and artillery, so they come, we definitely will be destroyed.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there was wooden huts and so on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So it's not safe.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then being in this house, beyond this-- this unfinished highway, it will be safer because there will be some protection.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we agree, and we took our small belongings, what we had, and we stay with this guy and this German woman who ran away from this place.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "She went to Salzburg or somewhere there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we stayed, and we wait until the Russians came.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And, of course, there was our good luck.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And, of course, you know, we had to hear this shooting and seeing how the chimneys were razed off by-- by the artillery and so on.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And then one day-- and we were not only-- but also some of the other French colleagues of this guy were also.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But these colleagues, they were on the first floor, and we slept in the-- in the basement.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "In the basement.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "There was a-- a finished basement, and there were beds, and we sleep there with this Italian guy.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So one day, one of these French guys from the upstairs came out of the house because suddenly the whole night, there was no shooting.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He came out and came back, and he was crying, [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH] So the Russians are here.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And definitely, indeed, we have seen how the Russian soldiers were climbing this unfinished highway and descending on our side.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
